Dependencies:

plugins-1.5.1.4
bitmap-opengl-0.0.0
stb-image-0.2
FTGL-1.333

Usage

* +/- (maximum zoom)
* cursor keys
* left mouse
* right mouse
* r key

The root of the contracted redex is colored red.

Reduction should export a function c_reduction of type DynamicReduction

Possible extensions:

* Zoom in and out with scroll wheel (would require freeglut)
* Open file dialog for reductions (would require GTK+ or wxWidgets)
* Different color schemes
* DSL for definition of reductions
